+cargo test
+PASS: 48 tests (16 executive, 6 ephemeris, 13 estimator, 6 authority,
+4 predictor, 3 types) plus all doc tests
+
+cargo clippy --all-targets -- -D warnings
+PASS
+
+cargo fmt --all -- --check
+PASS
+```
